#############################
# Requirements Gathering
#############################

# Functional Requirements:

Before installing/updating requires Admin permission


# Non-Functional Requirements:

interface pede pro usuario criar uma lista de apps para instalar a partir de um browser de ids.

pergunta configurações de instalação adicionais (menu iniciar, barra de tarefas, etc.)

instala os apps em ordem, avisando o progresso.

inicia e pega a lingua nativa do usuario, para instalar os apps na lingua correta



#############################
# DISCLAIMER
#############################
This project uses the python library "subprocess" to handle os related operations.

also, subprocess have some inconpatibilitys as listed below:

"Availability: not Android, not iOS, not WASI.
This module is not supported on mobile platforms or WebAssembly platforms."

therefore, any listed plataform will also automatically be incompatible with this project.

# DISCLAMER OF THE DISCLAMEIR 

actually, it uses winget in the command, so its windows only
(PS. take a look at nix, it seems to be the equivalent in linux/macos)